text: Bickham is an unincorporated community in Washington Parish, Louisiana, United States. The community is located W. of Franklinton, Louisiana. ==Name origin== The community name is derived from an early settler in the area. The Bickham family first settled Washington parish in the year 1799. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Washington Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana
title: Bickham, Louisiana
